meaning.en: (of man) blinded by anger or malice; infuriated; angry and jealous.
at ease; readily; in a manner of shifting readily.
unconscious, senseless (eg- as if lamenting the separation from one’s beloved one).
meaning.ne: अचेत, बेहोश, चेतनाशुन्य (जस्तै मायालु/प्रेमी/प्रेमिकाको विरहले आदि) ।

meaning.en: a Tibetan/Bhote/Sherpa; a Limbu word to denote them or their tribe.
meaning.ne: तिब्बति; भोटे; शेर्पा; लिम्बूभाषामा तिब्बती, भोटे वा शेर्पा जातिलाई बुझाउने शब्द ।

meaning.en: illusion; frenzy; mania; orgy; madness; insanity; craziness.
frenzied; maniac; wild; mad; insane; illusioned; violently mad

meaning.ne: हुस्सु/कुइरो लाग्नु; धुम्मिनु; बादल ढम्म लाग्नु/ मडारिनु ।

meaning.en: anywhere; all around; on all sides; pervasively.
a kind of precious stone, bluish in color.
[Phedape] mostach (human); whiskers (both human and non human).[
(M) man’s birth place as described in the Mundhum.
meaning.ne: मुन्धुममा वर्णित मान्छे उत्पन्न भएको थलो ।

meaning.en: the goddess who protects a man from stomach, spleen and heart disease.
meaning.ne: मानिसलाई पेट र मुटुको रोगबाट जोगाउने देवी ।

meaning.en: rules; regulations; procedure; rules and regulations.
the eagle/vulture deity/god; a deity in the form of the eagle which is believed to eat the offenders heart, benumb hid limbs and eventually causes boils and blisters appear on his body.
meaning.ne: चीलदेव, जसले रिसाउँदा मानिसको मुटु खाने र उसको हातखुट्टा झमझमाउने रोग लगाउने तथा पछि खटिराको पनि प्रकोप गराउछ भनी विश्वास गरिएको चीलको रूपमा रहने देवता ।

meaning.en: Dhatura, puppy seed. Datura stramonium; D. fistulosa.
smilingly; with a smile; wearing a smile; in a smiling manner.
unsteady inconstant; fickle; fidgety; restless; playful; agile.
in the manner of simultaneous movement of the worms, etc.
1. the all-pervasive darkness at the time of creation. 2. quietness; loneliness; quietude.
meaning.ne: १. सृष्टिको सुरुमा सर्वत्र व्याप्त) महाअन्धकार । २. सुनसान ।

meaning.en: to spread out sth on the ground; to underlay.
a special beer used in worship.
meaning.ne: पूजामा प्रयोग गरिने एक प्रकारको जाँडविशेष ।

meaning.en: 1. private; secret; confidential; clandestine. 2. slowly; slackly; by degrees. 3. whispering; secretly.
meaning.ne: १. साउती (गुप्त चालको) । २. बिस्तारै; मन्द गतिले । ३. खुसखुस, गुप्त चालाले; कानेखुसी गर्ने किसिमले ।

meaning.en: the first layer of the first rocks of creation.
meaning.ne: सृष्टिमा भएको पहिलो चट्टानको पहिलो तह ।

meaning.en: 1. great devoidness (prevalent before creation). 2. hollow; void.
three-stone stand for putting a cooking vessel over fire.
the deity who facilitates safe and timely delivery of a baby.
meaning.ne: बच्चालाई ठीक समयमा सुरक्षासाथ जन्म दिने देवी ।

meaning.en: 1. devoidness (prevalent before creation). 2. open and void (empty) sky; space.
power; might; vim; (mental and physical psychosomatic) strmeanth; capacity; virility.
(adj.) powerful; capable; virile; mighty; influential. (n.) (M) a well-known/famous male character in the Kiranti folklore.(
meaning.ne: वि.) शक्तिशाली; शक्तिमान । (ना.) किराती लोककथाको एक प्रसिद्ध पुरुष पात्र ।

meaning.en: 1. might; almightiness; omnipotence; supreme/ultimate power. 2. fire.
1. a small worm which lives in a whirl of dust. 2. a kind of medicinal plant. Bischoffia javanica.
meaning.ne: १. धूलोमा गुँडुल्किएर बस्ने एक प्रकारको सानो कीरो । २. कैंजल ।

meaning.en: a kind of grass (plant). Neyraudia madagascariensis.
to drop sth; to let fall sth.
incantation; charm; sacred formula; mystical verse.
glottal stop of Limbu alphabet; a phonetic symbol like this ( ᤹ ) in the Limbu or Sirijunga script (alphabet).
meaning.ne: कण्ठमुखी स्वरयन्त्रस्पर्शी ध्वनि; त्यस ध्वनिलाई बुझाउन लिम्बू वा सिरिजङ्गा लिपिको यस्तो ध्वनिक ( ᤹ ) चिन्ह ।

meaning.en: 1. to crush (dry or parched things) into powder. 2. to crush/press down (a fallen/knocked man as in wrestling). 3. (of click, bell etc) to sound/strike.
meaning.ne: १. (सुकेको वस्तु माडमुड पारी) धूलो पार्नु । २. (पछारिएको वा चित भएको मान्छेलाई कुस्तीमा झैं) माडमुड पार्नु । ३. बज्नु ।

meaning.en: 1. oral incantation carried for generations by the Limbu priests- Phedangma, Samba and Yebas. 2. oral traditions.
meaning.ne: १. फेदाङ्मा, साम्बा, येबाहरूले मुखमुखै भनी आएको मन्त्र । २. जनश्रुति ।

meaning.en: energy; strmeanth; power; prowess; might; vim; virility.
the sound fo playing/blowing/beating musical instruments; blowing/beating/resounding (sound of) musical instruments.
meaning.ne: बाजा घन्केको वा बजेको स्वर; बजाइ; घन्काइ; वादन ।

meaning.en: a kind of small red bird found at riverside.
meaning.ne: खोलातिर पाइने एक प्रकारको सानो र रातो चरो ।

meaning.en: penance; meditation; contemplation; concentration of mind.
with a jerk; smartly; sprightly; jauntily.
meaning.ne: जुरुक्क; एकै प्रयास वा झट्कामा उठ्ने वा उचाल्ने किसिमले ।

meaning.en: a kind of bamboo. Dendrocalamus strictus.
1. to try one’s level best; to do one’s utmost. 2. to be much encouraged/enthusiastic/excited.
meaning.ne: १. मच्चिनु; जोड गर्नु; तम्सनु; भरमग्दुर गर्नु । २. अति उत्साहित हुनु ।

meaning.en: thunderbolt; a figurative term used in the Mundhum denoting the thunderbolt.
meaning.ne: वज्र; वज्रलाई बुझाउन मुन्धुममा प्रयोग गरिने आलङ्कारिक शब्द ।

meaning.en: to murmur/utter/recite the mystical verse quietly; to pray; to recite incantation(s).
1. holy Kirant-Limbu scripture based on oral tradition. 2. scriptural knowledge. 3. myth; mythology.
meaning.ne: १. श्रुति-परम्परामा प्रचलित किरात-लिम्बू-धर्मशास्त्र । २. शास्त्र; ज्ञान । ३. मिथक ।

meaning.en: to forget; to lose remembrance of; not to remember.
1. disobedient; defiant; insolent; obstinate. 2. stupid; silly.
meaning.ne: १. अटेरी; भनेको कुरा नमान्ने । २. लठुवा; आफु पनि नजान्ने अरुले भनेको पनि नमान्ने ।

meaning.en: a Limbu word denoting the Tamang ethnic people.
meaning.ne: तामाङ; लिम्बूभाषामा तामाङ जातिलाई बुझाउने शब्द ।

meaning.en: exceedingly; excessively; too much; very much.
meaning.ne: अत्यन्त/धेरै गर्ने चालाले; निमिट्यान्न/टाकटुक गर्ने चालाले ।

meaning.en: long outer garment (of white cotton) worn by Kirant (Limbu) women.
meaning.ne: मेखली; लिम्बू किराँत स्वास्नीमान्छेको एक प्रकारको वस्त्रविशेष ।

meaning.en: widower (a man who has lost his wife by death and not married again).
widow (a woman who has lost her husband by death and not married again).
1. woe; mourning; bereavement; agony; sorrow. 2. grief; lamentation over a death.
distressing; painful; troublesome; sorrowful; miserable; afflictive.
1. the first woman of the creation who could conceive and give birth to offspring. 2. the first created woman (spouse) in the story of creation. 3. wife.
meaning.ne: १. गर्भधारण गर्न सक्ने सृष्टिको प्रथम स्त्री । २. सृष्टिको पहिली स्त्री । ३. पत्नी ।

meaning.en: maids-on-wedding; a bevy of women relatives esp her aunt and sisters waiting on the bride who, according to the Limbu custom, go along with the new bride to escort her to the groom’s house.
meaning.ne: लोकन्ती; लिम्बू संस्कृतिमा विवाहनिम्ति बेहुलीलाई बेहुलाको घर पुर्याउन जाने बेहुलीका फुपू, दिदी, बहिनी आदिको लस्कर ।

meaning.en: wife of one’s husband’s elder or younger brother.
elder or younger brother of one’s husband.
[Phedape] a prepositional/postpositional particle or suffix meaning ‘without’, ‘except’, ‘besides’, ‘deprived of’, ‘lacking’ etc.[
meaning.ne: फेदापे] सर्वनाम वा नाम पछाडि जोडिएर ‘विना’, ‘रहित’, ‘नभइ’, ‘नभइकन’ आदि अर्थ बुझाउने निपात ।

meaning.en: a kind of malarial tree (a variety of malarial Xanthoxylum hamiltonianum).
to be fat; to become fat; to fatten; to gain weight.
1. (of family, tribe, race, species, animals, etc) become extinct; to die out; to be finished. 2. exhaust; to run short; to run out of supply (of sth).
meaning.ne: १. (जाति, वंश, पशु, आदि) नाश हुनु; निर्मुल हुनु । २, सिद्धिनु; सकिनु; कुनै पनि प्रकारको सामाग्री सकिनु ।

meaning.en: 1. a kind of white crested bird which flies in group (a kind of Bulbul). 2. (of wheat, plant, weed, etc) to topple over; ot cuddle; to fall down. 3. (of goat, kids) to bleat.
meaning.ne: १. एक प्रकारको बगालमा हुने (जुरेली) चरा । २. गहुँ, झार आदि ढल्नु । ३. बोका बाख्रा कराउनु; म्याम्या गर्नु ।

meaning.en: or; otherwise; if not; or else; if.
1. to complete/accomplish/carry out fully. 2. to finish/do away with.
meaning.ne: १. सबै वा जम्मै टाकटुक सक्नु; सिद्ध्याउनु । २. सक्नु; सिद्ध्याउनु; निमिट्यान्न पार्नु ।

meaning.en: to fell/topple over; to get the bushes, etc depress by walking/treading upon them; to press sth; to tread over sth.
meaning.ne: धानकोदो झार आदि ढाल्नु; माडमुड पार्नु; दलदाल पार्नु ।

meaning.en: 1. to take control over sth; to take sth unauthoritatively into one’s possession. 2. to help/serve oneself. 3. to have a mutual talk; to have an exchange of talk.
meaning.ne: १. आफ्नो पार्नु; (अर्काको चिज वस्तु) कब्जा गर्नु । २. आफ्नो लागि कुनै काम/सेवा आफै गर्नु । ३. परस्परमा कुरा आदानप्रदान गर्नु ।

meaning.en: 1. value; cost; price. 2. a sentence particle denoting “if, then”.
meaning.ne: १. मूल्य; मोल; दाम । २. “नि, त, ता, तै, यदि” आदि वाक्यांशको अन्तमा आउने अनिसश्चयबोधक निपात शब्द ।

meaning.en: 1. ‘non not’, a negative particle when affixed before or after a verb gives a negative meaning. 2. no; not.
meaning.ne: १. हुनु क्रियालाई नकारात्मक बनाउन क्रियापदको अगाडि पछाडि जोडिने निपात । २. नाइँ; अहँ ।

meaning.en: pubic hair of the vagina; secret hair on the female organ; pubes of the vagina.
1. human-being; man. 2. the first man of creation.
meaning.ne: १. मानव; मान्छे; मानिस । २. सृष्टिको प्रथम पुरुष ।

meaning.en: in a manner of haste/doing one’s utmost.

1. a row/bevy/swarm of young woman/ladies. 2. females who wait on/escort the bride upto the groom’s house. 3. the constellation of the Great Bear, the pleiades. 4. a group of stars often visible in the morning beside the constellation of three stars.
meaning.ne: १. तरुनीको लहर/ताँती । २. लोकन्ती; बेहुलीलाई पुर्याउन जाने स्वास्नीमानिस । ३. सप्तर्षि तारा; कृत्तिका । ४. तीनआँख्ले तारासँगै अक्सर बिहानीपख गुजमुज्ज परेर रहने ताराहरुको समूह ।

meaning.en: 1. name of a high hill in the Milke Mountain Range in eastern Nepal. 2. one of the hill in the Milke Range, mentioned in the Mundhum.
meaning.ne: १. पूर्वी नेपालको मिल्के पहाड शृङ्खलाको एक उच्च डाँडाको नाम । २. मिल्के पहाड शृङ्खलामा अवस्थित मुन्धुममा वर्णित एक पहाड ।

meaning.en: 1. indeclinable, a polite word expressing humbleness denoting the sense of ‘at any rate’, ‘in any case’, ‘anyhow’, ‘even though’, ‘despite’, ‘knowingly or unknowingly’, ‘so so’ etc. 2. so so, simple; ordinary. 3. (even though) humbly; very simple; so-so.
meaning.ne: १. केहि कुरा अर्पण वा जाहेर गर्दा प्रसङ्गअनुसार ‘जे जस्तो भएपनि’, ‘नमिठो भएपनि’, ‘नराम्रो भएपनि’, ‘जानी नजानी’, ‘भए वा नभएपनि’ आदि विभिन्न अर्थ वहन गरी विनम्रता प्रकट गर्ने शब्द । २. साधारण । ३. अति सामान्य; यस्ते उस्तै (भएपनि) ।

meaning.en: (n.) imperfection; not full. (adv.) imperfectly; not fully.(
meaning.ne: ना.) अपूर्णता; अपूर्णत्व । (क्रिवि.) अपूर्ण रूपले; भरि नहुने गरेर ।

meaning.en: [Phedape] ‘no, not’, a negative particle; one of the negative forms of the verb ‘to be’.[
meaning.ne: फेदापे] ‘होइन’; ‘हुनु’ क्रियाको नकारार्थी भाव बुझाउने शब्द ।

meaning.en: a lot of; a large number of; many; excessive; innumerable.
meaning.ne: असङ्ख्य; धेरै; अत्यन्त; कता हो कता ।

meaning.en: 1. unsociable; not congenial; queer; eccentric. 2. different; separate; incomparable.
meaning.ne: १. कसैसित मिल्न नसक्ने; अडभङ्गे; अमिल्दो । २. बेग्लै; फरक; पृथक ।

meaning.en: 1. unfathomable; unapproachable; unattainable; unknowable; inaccessible. 2. devoid of quality.
meaning.ne: १. अगम; गम पाइ नसक्नु; जानि नसक्नु । २. निर्गुण ।

meaning.en: suddenly; abruptly; all of a sudden.

meaning.ne: नामको पछाडि जोडिएर ‘विना’, ‘रहित’, ‘नभई’ आदि अर्थ बुझाउने शब्द ।

meaning.en: 1. to tell/relate/narrate. 2. auxiliary/helping verb suffixed to another word to denote ‘to do sth’, ‘to impress or to be impressed’.
meaning.ne: १. भन्नु; सुनाउनु । २. अन्य शब्दको पछिल्तिर जोडिएर ‘केहि गर्नु’, ‘प्रभावित पार्नु/हुनु’ आदि अर्थ बोध गराउने सहायक क्रिया ।

meaning.en: to perform the final marriage-ritual to transfer a woman to her husband’s clan from her paternal clan.
a bit; a little; few; a little bit; scanty.
a village named Myalung in Limbu; one of villages in distant Far Kinant region, described in the Limbu legends and at present is the headquarter of Terhathum districh (east Nepal).
meaning.ne: लिम्बू पौराणिक आख्यनमा वर्णित, हाल तेह्रथुम जिल्लाको सदरमुकाममा पर्ने, पल्लो किराँतको एक गाउँको नाम ।

meaning.en: 1. to fall down; to have a fall; to drop/tumble. 2. (of prices) to decrease; to be less; to come down; to fall. 3. to be degraded/demoted.
meaning.ne: १. (माथिबाट) खस्नु; झर्नु । २. (भाउ आदि) कमी हुनु । ३. स्तर वा पद तल झर्नु ।

meaning.en: 1. (water etc) to heat/make hot. 2. to boil (milk, tea etc).
meaning.ne: १. तताउनु; तातो पार्नु । २. (दुध, चिया आदि) उमाल्नु; उमाल्ने प्रकृयाले पकाउनु ।

meaning.en: pink; pinkish; of light red color.
very much; many; considerable; nearly; almost.
mother; an address to the mother in thire person.
meaning.ne: आमा; आमालाई सङ्केत गरेर ‘आमा’ भनी तृतीय पुरुषका रूपमा भनिने शब्द ।

meaning.en: the nineteenth consonant letter of the Sirijunga alphabet.
a kind of edible and medicinal wild vegetable. Phytolaca acinosa.
(of wood, stone wall etc) to decay/rot; to collapse/fall down.
a kind of bacteria (which causes the clefts of the toes to rot); mowra-fat is used to cure it.(
meaning.ne: खुट्टाको चेपचाप कुहाउने) एक प्रकारको जीवाणु; जोत्ने कीरो, जसको उपचारका लागी चिउरीको तेल लगाइन्छ ।

meaning.en: in a manner of breaking or being chewed sth with a sound.
meaning.ne: मर्याकमर्याक आवाज आउने गरी चपाउने/भाँचिने चालाले ।

meaning.en: much; sufficient(ly); many; more; enough; abundant(ly).
in a manner of grinding of teeth or biting by cold.
1. seed (of crops). 2. husked millet grains washed for cooking to ferment it into millet beer. 3. weakness; feebleness.
meaning.ne: १. (अन्नको) बीउ । २. जाँड पकाउन धोइएको कोदो । ३. कमजोरी; दुर्बलता ।

meaning.en: 1. Yeba, a class of Limbu priest. 2. tickle; titillation. 3. edge; bank; border (of table, cot, river etc) 4. blade/edge (of a weapon). 5. or. that is.
meaning.ne: १. येबा; लिम्बू पुरोहितको एक वर्ग । २. कुतकुती; काउकुती । ३. छेउ; किनार; किनारा । ४. (हतियारको) धार । ५. अथवा ।

meaning.en: clay vessel with nine small holes in. the bottom, used in distilling wine.
meaning.ne: पैनी; रक्सी पार्दा प्रयोग गरिने पीँधमा नौवटा प्वाल भएको माटोको भाडो; पोटासी ।

meaning.en: one-seamed tinkling small bells worn by the Yeba behind his waist.
fried unhusked paddy (rice); such rice grains scattered about along the way during a funeral procession.

meaning.en: renowned martyr who reinvented and was dedicated to the development of the Kirant Limbu language and alphabet. He was assassinated at Martam village of West Sikkim in A.D. 1741 in  Rapdenchi Pemayonchi Monastery, by the conspiring Thachhang Lamas who were converting the Limbus to Buddhism. He is at present renowned as Sirijunga II.
